        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1933820925" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1339620252791769675">I picked this up because this guy was supposedly a great short story writer. Ugh okay. To me he’s like that friend of a friend who tells the worst stories that assumes you know the people in the story. But you don’t. And then crazy terrible stuff happens and you wish this guy would stop telling stories. But he rolls in to another on how he never learned to swim and you’re thanking god at least his stories are short. And you know something nutty is going to happen to this guy so when you hear he </span>
  <span id="freeText1339620252791769675" style="display:none">I picked this up because this guy was supposedly a great short story writer. Ugh okay. To me he’s like that friend of a friend who tells the worst stories that assumes you know the people in the story. But you don’t. And then crazy terrible stuff happens and you wish this guy would stop telling stories. But he rolls in to another on how he never learned to swim and you’re thanking god at least his stories are short. And you know something nutty is going to happen to this guy so when you hear he slept with some Soviet top dog’s wife and got sent to Siberia, you’re not exactly shocked.<br /><br />The only real difference is that there’s always livestock in Babel’s story.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="1339620252791769675" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
